## Assumptions and Limitations

### Assumptions

* Log returns better stabilize data for structural break modeling (confirmed by ADF test)
* The curated events are major influencers of price shifts

### Limitations

* Limited to 15 major events; smaller events may be excluded
* Event-price correlations do not imply causation (VAR models could improve analysis)
* Daily data granularity may miss intraday impacts

